Games for Watch
Over 30 games for Apple Watch.
Tic Tac Toe
Classic Tic Tac Toe game with options to turn on/off sound and selection of starting player (User, Watch, Alternate, Random). Statistics screen
                    to display number of wins, losses, and draws.
Whack-A-Bug
Whack as many bugs you can in 30 second. Top scores screen displays the top five scores and settings screen to enable/disable sound.
Memory Match
Match 8 pairs of images in one minute to win the game. Eight image themes and settings to enable or disable sound.
Sliding Blocks
Move image pieces to produce the final picture. Choice of three images and settings to enable or disable sound.
Privacy Policy:
This app does not collect user data.
